---
title: Crispy Roasted Salmon and Broccoli with Buttery Green Pea Rice and Lemony Mayo
description: Crunchy golden breadcrumbs make this easy baked salmon a fast family favourite! Our DIY lemony mayo is great dolloped onto the salmon and as a dipper for broccoli.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saumon-roti-croustillant-06a19a0c.jpg
